PART 1: THE ROSETTA STONE — INDEPENDENCE POLYS AT x=2
========================================================================

PATH: I(P_m, 2) = J(m+2) [Jacobsthal]
  I(P_ 0, 2) =      1 = J(2) = (2^2-(-1)^2)/3 ✓
  I(P_ 1, 2) =      3 = J(3) = (2^3-(-1)^3)/3 ✓
